<h1 align="center">ECHO OF ANCIENT MOSAICS</h1>
<p align="center"><img src="https://www.grandtourexperience.com/img/4625/or/n.jpg" width=500></p>
<p align="center">Are you ready for a journey through the world of ancient art, fascinating history and unsolved mysteries? It's just one click away!</p>
<p align="center">[[GET STARTED|Beginning_1]]</p>


:: Beginning_1 {"position":"600,375","size":"100,100"}
<h2 align="center">Welcome</h2>
<p align="center">You are on the threshold of the mosaic collection at the National Archaeological Museum of Naples. It is a unique treasure, showcasing some of the finest examples of ancient Roman mosaic art. Primarily sourced from the ruins of Pompeii, Herculaneum, and other sites in Campania, these mosaics date from the 2nd century BC to the 1st century AD and offer a vivid glimpse into the artistic mastery of the period.</p>
<p align="center">[[CONTINUE|Beginning_2]]</p>



